description: This file defines an API interface for managing 'partners' via HTTP requests, providing methods for listing, retrieving, creating, updating, and removing partners.

methods.name: list
methods.description: Fetches a list of partners with optional query parameters.

methods.name: get
methods.description: Retrieves details of a specific partner by ID.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Creates a new partner with provided data.

methods.name: update
methods.description: Updates an existing partner identified by ID with new data.

methods.name: remove
methods.description: Deletes a partner identified by ID.
